#: ../usage/env.rst:314 ../usage/env.rst:395 ../usage/env.rst:679
#: ../usage/env.rst:800
msgid "**Default:** ``[]``"
msgstr ""

#: ../usage/env.rst:151
msgid ""
"Set by ``fab`` to the full host list for the currently executing command. "
"For informational purposes only."
msgstr ""
"由 fab 设置的当前正在执行命令的主机列表。仅用于显示信息。"

#: ../usage/env.rst:154 ../usage/env.rst:204 ../usage/env.rst:307
